document_data.caption: A map showing the Cambrent Gap on Gwynneth.
document_data.name: Cambrent Gap
document_data.mainbody: The '''Cambrent Gap''' was a mountain pass located on the island of [[Gwynneth]] within the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite interactive atlas}}{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: The Moonshae Isles}}
document_data.Geography: The Cambrent Gap split the [[Cambro Mountains]] toward their northern end. The pass connected the eastern edge of [[Myrloch Vale]] with eastern Gwynneth.
